---
title: Carb Smart Toasted Chana Dal on Paneer with Peaches and Mint-Cucumber Sauce
description: This inspired salad sees paneer pan fried, then slathered with fig jam and topped with chana dal before getting a quick turn in the oven to get those caramelized edges. Fresh, sweet summer peaches offer a refreshing flair along with mint-cucumber sauce.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chana-dal-rotie-et-paneer-8d852264.jpg
